        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "在过去 {{warranty.years}} 年内购买过产品。",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.10-warranty.page.page1.block.8.item.1"
            },
            {
              "text": "有原始订单号或购买时使用的电子邮件。",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.10-warranty.page.page1.block.8.item.2"
            },
            {
              "text": "如通过经销商或零售合作伙伴购买，须提供原始收据的副本。",
              "text_id": "content.chapter.10-warranty.page.page1.block.8.item.3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "向我们发送电子邮件申请保修服务：**{{brand.support_email}}**",
          "text_id": "content.chapter.10-warranty.page.page1.block.9.text"
